{
  "texts": [
    "The synthesized framework proposed in this section is a partial development cycle; however, practitioners can gain vital insights from it.",
    "Our analysis of the interview data reveals that users mostly need explanations if they come across unfamiliar content or experience feelings of online insecurity or curiosity regarding the recommender system.",
    "These identified problems stimulate a need to collect the design requirements.",
    "However, apart from the \"identified problems\" in this work, several others may also exist if the issue is considered from a broader perspective or for other AI-based systems.",
    "Our analysis in this paper shows that design requirements, such as explanations, should be concise, summarized, and non-technical descriptions."
  ]
}